name: Final Fantasy Legends: Jikuu no Suisho
name_original: Final Fantasy Legends: Jikuu no Suisho
description:
Final Fantasy Legends: Jikuu no Suisho is a RPG game developed by Square Enix. It was originally released in 2015. It was published by Square Enix.
Final Fantasy Legends: Jikuu no Suisho is available on iOS and Android.
